# pipenv
#   According to pypa/pipenv#598, it is recommended to include Pipfile.lock in git.
#   However, in case of collaboration, it may be optional.
#   https://pipenv.pypa.io/en/latest/advanced/#pipenv-and-version-control
#Pipfile.lock

# poetry
#   Similar to Pipfile.lock, poetry.lock is optionally ignored in git.
#   https://python-poetry.org/docs/basic-usage/#commit-your-poetrylock-file-to-version-control
#poetry.lock

